---
title: Breaded Parmesan Chicken Tenders with Honey Dijonnaise and Roasted Broccoli
description: Crispy Parm-coated chicken cooked to golden perfection is a perennial family fave! This version is made even better with a honey-Dijon mayo dip and garlicky mashed potatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/filets-de-poulet-parmesan-4d81ea0a.jpg
